name: BVC:010
description:
"I had the privilege of being blessed with the presence, wisdom and love of one of the strongest ladies on this earth. Cecelia Ann Clark who was diagnosed with breast cancer twice and fought both times. She was a woman who wouldn't let the disease define her or slow her down. She continued to be the funny, sassy, never hold anything back woman my family & I knew and loved. May 11, 2011 God called this wonderful woman home and although I'd give anything to have her here with me, I know you're watching over me. So this October in honor of Breast Cancer Awareness Month I dedicate the BVC collection to a woman who was not only just a grandmother, but a bestfriend, a teacher, a survivor and most importantly my guardian angel." -Basia V. Clark

*10mm fuchsia, creme & carnation pink gemstones 
*Finished toggle clasp 
*Silver plated bail 
*Silver plated ribbon 
*SIZE: sm/ md (7.25in clasp to clasp) 
*Stretches for maximum wrist comfort 
*TYPE: singlet

Hand crafted by LR *Goods 100% American made

Please allow 3-4 business days for item to be shipped after payment has cleared.
